Pre-Game Insights: Mitchell Marsh will lead Australia despite the return of seamer Pat Cummins.
Mitchell Santner will captain New Zealand.
Regular captain Kane Williamson will miss the series expecting the birth of his third child.
New Zealand will also miss all-rounder Daryl Mitchell owing to an injury.
Australia enter the series after a 2-1 T20I series win at home against the West Indies.
New Zealand routed Pakistan in their previous T20I series by a 4-1 margin.
